>园区湖东社工委、三星半导体、行政审批局等13家试点单位参与运行。</span></span></p></section></section></section><section class="_editor"><p><br  /></p></section><p style="letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;"><img class="" data-ratio="0.60375" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/HJ0xHGjg8S0Pqn7fuEeFL0xzy5OPadc2afAADxMouvbxic8KQcNNXZe3JmdYltNOTt0MgnUnUvibccYsAuhdITRQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="800" style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:36px;;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: justify;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;word-wrap: break-word !important;width: 677px !important;visibility: visible !important;"></p><p><br  /></p><p style="letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;text-align: center;"><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;">下周，智慧党建平台</span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;text-align: center;"><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;">即将正式全面上线</span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;text-align: center;"><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;">为确保各级党组织顺利使用</span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;text-align: center;"><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;">保证平台发挥应有作用</span></p><p style="letter-spacing: 2px;line-height: 2em;text-align: center;"><span style="font-size:14px;line-height:34px;;"><br  /></span></p><p><img class="" data-copyright="0" data-ratio="0.75" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/dtKt6iawKSvmUb6vXvfKrEwVtfyyLicemXkNdtcKrNFIC8eJmBwjON3ib1qb3MzaluobqWPbB94pwQibkUVF6ZpSaw/640?wx_fmt=gif" data-type="gif" data-w="800" style=""></p><p><br  /></p><section class="_editor"><section style="display: flex;justify-content: center;"><section style="margin-right:-5px;margin-left:10px;margin-top: 10px;width: 1